metadata.name: Cool Girl NFT #021 FanArt
metadata.description:
imotoさんのCool Girl NFT #021ちゃんのファンアートです。

オイルを塗ってもらうのだって、「我が道を往く」Cool Girl

日差しが照り続けるビーチで
「オイル…塗って！」と強気ながらも
どこか恥ずかしげな感じがする瞬間…

This is a fan art of the 021st girl, "Cool Girl NFT" run by imoto.
She makes a cool gesture to get oiled.
On the beach under the sun, she says, "Oil...oil me! she says.
I drew her in a moment of strength, but with a hint of shyness.
